GIMP JPEG-2000 plugin
=====================

To build and install it :

1. Ensure you have installed required dependancies, then build using :

	./configure
	make
	make install



Dependancies
============

1. Gimp plugin SDK: libgimp2.0-dev
2. Openjpeg library 1.2 from http://www.openjpeg.org/index.php?menu=download


